item.title: CVE-2014-9921|2024-08-06T14:02:36.827Z -- intel -- cloud%20analysis%20and%20deconstructive%20services%20%28cads%29
item.description: Information disclosure vulnerability in McAfee (now Intel Security) Cloud Analysis and Deconstructive Services (CADS) 1.0.0.3x, 1.0.0.4d and earlier allows remote unauthenticated users to view, add, and remove users via a configuration error.
